meta_keywords: Feature Movies in the Public Domain
data.meta_description: From IMDb: Two members of a show troupe are murdered, and Charlie Chan is called in to solve the case. Stars: Sidney Toler, Mantan Moreland, Victor Sen Young, Tanis Chandler, Larry Blake, Kirk Alyn, Rita Quigley, and Anne Nagel This is the last of twenty-two Charlie Chan movies starring Sidney Toler. This movie can also be found here.
